trans-unit.source: Represents the addition of a <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> during dynamic update.
trans-unit.target: Representa a adição de um <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> durante a atualização dinâmica.
Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: This class can be used by a tracking service to determine which <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>s have been added during a dynamic update.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe pode ser usada por um serviço de controle para determinar qual <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>s foram adicionados durante uma atualização dinâmica.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>

trans-unit.source: An instance of this object is generated for every <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet> that is added (that is, that did not exist in the workflow prior to this dynamic update).
trans-unit.target: Uma instância do objeto é gerada para cada <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>que é adicionada (ou seja, que não existia no fluxo de trabalho antes dessa atualização dinâmica).</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.AddedRuleSetAction"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.AddedRuleSetAction"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.AddedRuleSetAction"></xref> class by using the new <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.AddedRuleSetAction"> </xref> classe usando o novo <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> is a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> é uma referência nula (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> no Visual Basic).
